<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Form Submission</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #fff5f7;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffebee, #ffe6f0);
            padding: 20px;
            margin: auto;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #f8bbd0;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ffcdd2;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .header h2 {
            color: #e91e63;
        }

        .content {
            color: #444;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .content a {
            color: #d81b60;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .content a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #888;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #c2185b;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(194, 24, 91, 0.4);
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #ad1457;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">

        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Thank You for Reaching Out!</h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>

            <p>Thank you for contacting us at <strong>Foodies's Heaven</strong>!</p>

            <p>We have received your message:</p>
            <p><em>"<%= message %>"</em></p>

            <p>We appreciate your feedback and are currently looking into your query. Our team will get back to you as
                soon as possible to assist you.</p>

            <p>If your matter is urgent, please feel free to reach out to us directly at
                <a href="mailto:support@foodiesheaven.com">support@foodiesheaven.com</a>.
            </p>

            <p>Thank you for choosing Foodies's Heaven!</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br><strong>The Foodies's Heaven Team</strong></p>

            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
                <a href="https://www.foodiesheaven.com" class="cta-button">Visit Foodies's Heaven</a>
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Foodies's Heaven. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8em;">This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
